From fa1be9523d569adfe207c85a1e44f074172bc305 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Maksim Ivanov <emaxx@google.com>
Date: Thu, 9 Oct 2025 14:16:00 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Support for LLVM 22 (#373)

Make clang_delta work with LLVM tip-of-the-tree as of 2025-10-08. Update the
CI-LLVM-Nightly bot to build&test against LLVM 22.
